jsx.ui.layout
Class AbsoluteLayout

java.lang.Object
  js.Disposable
      jsx.Configurable
          jsx.ui.Container.Layout
              jsx.ui.layout.AbsoluteLayout
Direct Known Subclasses:
BorderLayout, CardLayout, FlowLayout
public class AbsoluteLayout
extends Container.Layout

Layouts children of a container in a flow.

Note, A FlowLayout layout is composed of BarLayout layouts although a BarLayout is also a FlowLayout.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org
